{"tid":374363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"容易動心嘅傻仔入黎共鳴一下","createTime":"2017-08-25T16:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T23:47:32.000Z","uid":138557,"like":97,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17f20c489c416c61a70570c549af02664574ab49","tid":374363,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"見到個樣好睇嘅, 就FF同佢拍拖嘅情景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樣唔係特別好嘅, 只要對我nice少少就令我FF一頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我鍾意好多人, 好想同佢地瘋狂拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我花心但我唔濫, 未出過軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為冇拖拍&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n想聽下同類人嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abe528ed3b2fdaef0e6bfe70328b4eb084f35ed","tid":374363,"uid":137659,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03a4314224d280caf22fb27d91e5c697053e97ed","tid":374363,"uid":127116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:26:04.000Z","msg":"好易會沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5af0888a21b74fd8e0b11c9c063e89e3442dc6","tid":374363,"uid":138557,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為講緊人地對你好少少就會好心動 變到自己好上心 我都係出返去先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係會上心，之前都試過，佢樣就一般，但人真係超nice，果時暗戀同明接近左佢好耐，但係佢有一日同我講我追到個對象，開始拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，結果我果斷斬纜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(我可能一開始講得唔清楚，sor"},{"pid":"553d38bc57fe610884fdcd56151ea57d2032e495","tid":374363,"uid":138557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好易會沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c